'''''Star Wars Insider'' 43''' is the forty-third issue of ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' magazine. It was published in [[April]] [[1999]]. Three cover variants were available for issue 43: a newsstand version featuring [[Qui-Gon Jinn/Legends|Qui-Gon Jinn]], a subscriber-exclusive version featuring [[Darth Maul/Legends|Darth Maul]], and a Previews Exclusive version similar to the subscriber version but with different coloring for the ''Star Wars Insider'' logo.

==Contents==
===Departments===
*From the Editor's Desk {{C|by Jon Bradley Snyder}}
*[[Rebel Rumblings]]
*[[Prequel Update]]: The Characters of Episode I ''The Phantom Menace''
*[[Prequel Profile]] &mdash; [[David Tattersall]] {{C|by [[Jamie Painter]]}}
*[[Star News]] {{C|by Scott Chernoff}}
*[[In the Star Wars Universe|In the'' Star Wars ''Universe]] &mdash; [[Paul Blake]] {{C|by [[Matt Yeo]]}}
*[[The Horse's Mouth|Straight from the Horse's Mouth]] &ndash; Episode I Comics: The Double-Bladed Saber {{C|by [[Peet Janes]]}}
*[[Scouting the Galaxy]] &ndash; Build Your Own Universe {{C|by [[Stephen J. Sansweet]]}}
*[[The Jawa Trader|Jawa Trader]]
*[[The Last Page]]

===Features===
*"[[Brian Blessed: A Blessed Event]] {{C|by [[Scott Chernoff]]}}
*:<small>As [[Boss/Legends|Boss]] [[Rugor Nass/Legends|Nass]], leader of the [[Gungan/Legends|Gungans]], actor Brian Blessed looms large over [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|Episode I]]—even though we never see his real face. Blessed tells the ''Insider''{{'s}} [[Scott Chernoff]] who's the Boss.</small>
*"[[George Lucas Down Under]] Part II"
*:<small>In the conclusion of our coverage of George Lucas' meeting with the Australian press, he talks about the origins of ''[[Star Wars]]'', and the future of the saga.</small>
*"[[Droids of Episode I]]" {{C|by [[Daniel Wallace]]}}
*:<small>They're all here—from familiar friends like [[Astromech droid/Legends|astromech (R2) droids]] and [[Protocol droid/Legends|protocol droids]] (like [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]]), to new foes like [[Droid starfighter/Legends|starfighter droids]] and [[DRK-1 Dark Eye probe droid/Legends|Sith probes]]—it's an exclusive guide to the droids of ''The Phantom Menace'' from [[Daniel Wallace]], author of [[The Essential Guide to Droids|''Star Wars: The Essential Guide to Droids'']].</small>
*"[[Decipher: The Thrill of Victory]]" {{C|by [[Ryan Morris]]}}
*:<small>They came, they saw, the conquered. Ryan Morris takes ''Insider'' readers inside the 1998 Decipher ''Star Wars'' [[Star Wars Customizable Card Game|Customizable Card Game]] Championship Tournament, where it really is how you play the game.</small>
*"[[Lucasfilm Lifers]]" {{C|by [[Kevin Fitzpatrick]]}}
*:<small>From the model shop to the executive suite, meet the magnificent seven who have been with Lucasfilm from the first [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|Star Wars movie]]'' through the latest. The ''Insider''{{'s}} [[Kevin Fitzpatrick]] tells us why they stayed in that galaxy far, far away.</small>

